OL,3,CStarmer says boys found guilty of rape
OL,4,Cwill have sentences reviewed
OL,6,FSir Keir Starmer has said the
OL,7,FFordingbridge rape case which saw two
OL,8,Fteenage boys avoid jail sentences will
OL,9,Fgo to the Court of Appeal.
OL,11,FTwo girls were raped in the Hampshire
OL,12,Ftown by two 15-year-olds - who cannot
OL,13,Fbe named for legal reasons.
OL,15,FThey were both given non-custodial
OL,16,Fsentences by a judge at Southampton
OL,17,FCrown Court who said he wanted to
OL,18,F"avoid criminalising these children
OL,19,Funnecessarily".
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/6
