PN,41503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1779872682
OL,3,CStarmer says boys found guilty of rape
OL,4,Cwill have sentences reviewed
OL,6,FSpeaking on Tuesday during a visit to
OL,7,FEast Sussex, Sir Keir confirmed that
OL,8,FLord Hermer had decided the sentences
OL,9,Fcould now be reviewed at the Court of
OL,10,FAppeal.
OL,12,FHe said: "There are questions about
OL,13,Fthe sentence.
OL,15,F"The attorney general has power to
OL,16,Frefer a case to a court of appeal if
OL,17,Fthe attorney general thinks that the
OL,18,Fsentence is too lenient.
OL,20,F"The attorney general has now
OL,21,Fexercised that power.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
