FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1779872682
OL,3,CStarmer says boys found guilty of rape
OL,4,Cwill have sentences reviewed
OL,6,F"So I can announce that case now will
OL,7,Fgo to a Court of Appeal... and that is
OL,8,Fclearly the right outcome."
OL,10,FThe prime minister described the case
OL,11,Fas "really distressing," adding: "I
OL,12,Fthink it's distressing for everybody
OL,13,Fto see, to hear about.
OL,15,F"The courage, frankly, of the girls to
OL,16,Fcome forward is humbling, but it is
OL,17,Fdistressing.
OL,19,F"I find it distressing as a
OL,20,Fpolitician. I find it distressing as a
OL,21,Ffather."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
