PN,41505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1779872682
OL,3,CStarmer says boys found guilty of rape
OL,4,Cwill have sentences reviewed
OL,6,FLord Hermer said he had directed his
OL,7,Fofficials to "work urgently to allow
OL,8,Fme to consider this decision swiftly"
OL,9,Fdue to the "huge amount" of public
OL,10,Finterest that the case had generated.
OL,12,FHe said: "It is clear to me from their
OL,13,Fpowerful personal statements that
OL,14,Fthese girls have displayed immense
OL,15,Fbravery in coming forward.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
